      "topic": "Any questions about gameplay functions that need concrete answers, no matter how small. Every little bit helps us all get a little closer to an accurate translation.\n# Please do not answer questions without absolute certainty or, ideally, evidence.\nAnswers may be effectively taken as gospel, and used to update gameplay text."
